page.title: 13WILDLIFE IN WALSGRAVE
page.content: In Walsgrave there is not much wildlife,but behind Asda there is a variety of wildlife.There is a lot of wasteland there where animals can roam around.There is a lot of farming land there.Many species are starting to grow on the farmland. When I explored the countryside I saw a variety of butterflies.They were all different colours.I also saw a number of fox and rabbit holes,but I never saw them running about. There were a lot of trees on the landscape.All of them looked the same shape and size.At night you can see the animals running about. There is not a variety of flowers in Walsgrave.Daisies and roses are the most common you can see.We found that in Walsgrave there is not much wildlife but around Asda there is.
